About this site

I am Anna Tseng, a Year 3 School of Computing and Information Systems student majoring in Smart-City Management and Technology at Singapore Management University (SMU). As part of IS415 Geospatial Analytics and Applications AY2022-23 Semester 2, this website was created to document and showcase the varied geospatial analytics methods learned under the guidance of Prof Kam Tin Seong.
